Herbaliz Fine Facial Oil, Rosewood & Ginger

Brand: Herbaliz

Category: Facial Moisturizer/Treatment

Ingredients: Helianthus Annuus (Sunflower) Seed Oil*, Calendula Officinalis (Pot Marigold)*, Plantago Major (Plantain)*, Symphytum Officinale (Comfrey) Leaf*, Rose Hips Seed Oil*, Oenothera Biennis (Evening Primrose) Oil*, Aniba Rosodora (Rosewood)

Rosodora (Rosewood) Oil, Zingiber Officinale (Ginger) Oil*, Lavandula Angustifolia (Lavender) Oil*, Tocopherol.*Certified Organic

Directions: Start with one or two drops on clean fingertips. Dot on face and neck; gently smooth into skin. Use morning and evening as a moisturizer to improve your skin's texture and radiance. Apply to wet skin to add

y to wet skin to add moisture. A spritz with an Herbaliz Moisture Mist, Skin Refresher, or some mineral water beforehand would be nice.

Warnings: No preservatives. Keep away from heat and sun. Not for internal use. Keep out of eyes. Use within one year of purchase.
